text.__SUMMARY__: Shorea subcylindrica is a species of plant in the Dipterocarpaceae family. It is a tree endemic to Borneo.
text.Sources: Ashton, P. (1998). "Shorea subcylindrica". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T33435A9784213. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T33435A9784213.en. Retrieved 22 December 2017.
